description: Silver Grail Resources Ltd., an exploration stage company, engages in the acquisition and exploration of mineral properties primarily in the Stewart region of northwestern British Columbia, Canada. The company explores for cobalt, silver, gold, copper, zinc, and molybdenum minerals. Silver Grail Resources Ltd. was founded in 1979 and is headquartered in Victoria, Canada.
ceo: Dr. Dino M. Cremonese J.D., L.L.B., LL.B., P.Eng.
